nial+Series&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Utah+Press&amp;rft.date=1988&amp;rft_id=info%3Aoclcnum%2F18106573&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-60781-151-0&amp;rft.aulast=Peterson&amp;rft.aufirst=Levi+S.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALevi+S.+Peterson\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite id=\"CITEREFPeterson1990\" class=\"citation\">&#8212;&#8212; (1990), <i>Night Soil: New Stories</i>, Signature Books, <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/1560850035\" title=\"Special:BookSources/1560850035\">1560850035</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/OCLC\" title=\"OCLC\">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.worldcat.org/oclc/21873653\">21873653</a></cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Night+Soil%3A+New+Stories&amp;rft.pub=Signature+Books&amp;rft.date=1990&amp;rft_id=info%3Aoclcnum%2F21873653&amp;rft.isbn=1560850035&amp;rft.aulast=Peterson&amp;rft.aufirst=Levi+S.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALevi+S.+Peterson\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite id=\"CITEREFPeterson1995\" class=\"citation\">&#8212;&#8212; (1995), <i>Aspen Marooney</i>, Signature Books, <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/1560850787\" title=\"Special:BookSources/1560850787\">1560850787</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/OCLC\" title=\"OCLC\">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.worldcat.org/oclc/33166649\">33166649</a></cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Aspen+Marooney&amp;rft.pub=Signature+Books&amp;rft.date=1995&amp;rft_id=info%3Aoclcnum%2F33166649&amp;rft.isbn=1560850787&amp;rft